<h3>CAREER</h3>
<p>Upon completion of the study program at the American University in Bosnia and Herzegovina, doctoral students gain an accredited diploma in the EU, Turkey and Bosnia and Herzegovina, which provides them with the opportunity to develop a successful career. In recent years, the labor market recorded a very large increase in interest for experts in the field of computer engineering. Computer Engineering program covers almost all areas of the industrial sector of information technology, and therefore a wide choice of future career. Doctoral students who successfully complete this study, may perform: entrepreneurship, development of web applications, database management, artificial intelligence, computer management and information systems, computer systems analysis, etc. Doctoral students can also continue a successful career in government institutions and non-governmental organizations.</p>
<h3>CAREER PATHS</h3>
<p>State institutions, international organizations, NGOs, companies, web development solutions. Employment is possible locally, regionally and internationally.</p>
